column5: I'm at McRae and the launch ramp is not conducive to my boat any others in the area anyone knows of that are reasonably priced not like starport marina at $20 in and $20 out  want to take the family out for a fish Without breaking the bank
Just drive into Orilla there are 2 both free,1 on Simcoe right on #12 the other on Couch at the town docks (much better launch)
Are you staying at McRae provinal park  if so and want to go out fishing I have my boat in the water and yea the Launch here sucks I am on site 119
Monte Reno has a launch and it's pretty reasonable. Close to cooks for a fish or the laker grounds.
